onsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=94.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=88.topic"> Next Topic >> </a> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=95%><tr><td bgcolor=#000000><table border=0 width=100% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><tr><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Author</font></td><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(3/6/01 7:51:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Scynthian Party Hut</span><hr size=1> Alysia smiled. (This takes place a few days after the Funeral of Wulf.) She reached up in the hut hanging small decorations on the wall. Her belly was already getting bigger which made it a bit more difficult for her to do things. She then finished the decorations and walked over to the food table. It was full of fresh fuits, salads, and nutbread, a special family recipe. She leaned down to spell the foods and smiled as she walked over to the bar and sighed as she knew that her sisters would be able to drink yet she could not because of the baby. Curse it all!<br>
<br>
&quot;I hope we can get started soon.&quot;<br>
<br>
Above the entrance to the door it had two large banners that read:<br>
<br>
'Happy Late Birthday Aly&quot;<br>
and<br>
'It's a Girl!'<br>
<br>
She smiled hoping the party would go well. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulacacora.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LaCa Cora</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(3/8/01 3:45:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scynthian Party Hut</span><hr size=1> The banners above the door made her grin a little bit as she stepped, or waddle, inside.  Carrying a rather favorable mound of presents.. she set them down quickly, then arching back a little bit and placing her hand on her lower back.  Presents being two scrolls (hand-written by Julian--One on the most laughable Roman Senate events ((Like Caesar and Marc Antony becoming drunk and stripping)) and one on the life of Alysia herself.}, an original copy of Pompey's retirement scroll from Rome (Ah, the air is sweet again), and a small colourful box, containing a necklace with tiny circular golden pieces, each inscribed with a member of the Loire family, from Sayler to two blank coins in which the latest children will be added onto.<br>
<br>
&quot;By the Gods if time doesn't kill me, this child will.&quot; <br>
<br>
Sighing a bit, she stepped over and kissed her mothers cheek.<br>
<br>
&quot;Happy of both days, Mother.  I've brought you some gifts, from Rome of course, so just pretend you like them and everything will be fine.&quot;<br>
<br>
Flashing her mother a smile, she sat down, relaxing her poor feet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#993300>(3/8/01 10:31:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scynthian Party Hut</span><hr size=1> She smiles at her daughter.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hush yourself Cora. I would love anything that you bring me.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled leaning over giving her daughter a big hug. Looks really funny with both of their bellies all huge. LOL.<br>
<br>
&quot;Sorry the party's not more. . . fun. But you're the only person who has showed so far.&quot;<br>
<br>
Sighs. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#993300>(3/9/01 6:44:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scynthian Party Hut</span><hr size=1>  Dawn flipped from the rafters, her gift hidden on her body. For this event weapons were removed..and I mean every last one of those daggers..and toys. Releasing a soft war cry as she landing onto the table she smiled.<br>
<br>
 &quot;Okay I'm here..were's the action?&quot;<br>
<br>
 Dawn grinned evily as she extended her hand,and arm band sat gently in her palm, the center was a ruby shaped like a wolf, and the band was silver with golden barbed wire. <br>
<br>
 In the other palm she held out was well ironically a belly chain. It was silver, and on the end held an emerald and diamond dagger as a weight.<br>
<br>
 &quot;Happy birthday Happy Babyday..Happy everything the war is over&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#993300>(3/9/01 7:45:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scynthian Party Hut</span><hr size=1> Alysia chuckled at Dawn.<br>
<br>
&quot;I didn't ask for a stripper but what the heck.&quot;<br>
<br>
She sat down in front of the table and laughed.<br>
<br>
&quot;Gods Dawn!&quot; Looked at the band and bellychain she held to her.<br>
<br>
&quot;This must have cost so much!&quot;<br>
<br>
Eyes bugging out by now. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugalaciaelizabethofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GalaciaElizabeth of Scynthia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=file:///C:/My%20Documents/gabrielle_40.art BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#993300>(3/9/01 8:15:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scynthian Party Hut</span><hr size=1> *Galacia poked her head quietly around the door, then jumped in the door,striking a pose*&quot;The Party starts here!!!!&quot;*looking around puzzled* &quot;Where's everyone at?&quot; &quot;Oh, I brought you something.&quot; *walking towards Alysia,Galacia reached into her bag first  bringing out a small hand carved wooden horse* &quot;This one is for the baby, I carved it myself.&quot; *And then slowly revealing a necklace, with bright colorful seashells* &quot;I didn't make this one, but I thought it was really pretty so I...Well I didn't know really what to bring you,so I hope you like the gifts.&quot; &quot;Anyway,Happy Birth/Babyday!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 63<br> <font color=#993300>(3/10/01 6:56:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scynthian Party Hut</span><hr size=1>  Dawn chuckled as she looked at Aly, plopping down before her.<br>
<br>
 &quot;Its in appropriate for an Amazon to strip...but I can!&quot;<br>
<br>
 Smiling lightly she canted her head toward Aly.<br>
<br>
 &quot;I'm very talented.. for certain people that is.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Dawn smiled lightly, watching Aly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=queenalysia>Queen Alysia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC= http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif  BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 194<br> <font color=#993300>(3/12/01 12:23:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Party Time!</span><hr size=1> Alysia smiled to her sisters that came to celebrate her birthday and the future birth of her child.<br>
<br>
&quot;Alright, I want to get to these presents.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled and placed the necklace that Cora gave her, around her neck. She smiled looking down to the last two blank ones that needed to be filled.<br>
<br>
She then smiled at Dawn and took the wired arm band and slid it up her right arm, right underneath the mark of the amazon queen she had tattooed on her arm.<br>
<br>
She then smiled taking the belly chain and laughing as she attempted to put it on.<br>
<br>
&quot;I think this will have to wait until the baby is born.&quot; Chuckled.<br>
<br>
She smiled to Galacia and took the wooden horse. <br>
<br>
&quot;Thank you Galacia, I am sure she'll love it.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then looked over the seashell necklace and smiled putting it on. Both of her necklaces looked well together on her. She smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;Thank you all so much. This means the world to me!&quot;<br>
<br>
She sat up and hugged each of them one at a time.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
